						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Central Location</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Ryde is perfectly positioned with easy access to multiple hospitals and specialist facilities, including Macquarie University Hospital.</p>
