					<p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Psychological support is crucial for long-term bariatric surgery success. Many patients benefit from counseling both before and after surgery to address emotional eating, body image, and lifestyle changes.</p>

					<p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3"><strong>Support Services Available:</strong></p>
